<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Password Reset OTP</title>
</head>
<body>
    <div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;">
        <h1>Password Reset Verification</h1>
        <p>Hi {{name}},</p>
        <p>You have requested to reset your password. To proceed, please use the one-time password (OTP) below:</p>
        
        <div style="
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 24px;
            letter-spacing: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        ">
            {{otp}}
        </div>
        
        <p>This one-time password will expire in {{expirationMinutes}} minutes.</p>
        
        <p style="margin-top: 20px;">
            <strong>Note:</strong> If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact our support team.
        </p>
        
        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 30px;">
            If you're having trouble, please copy and paste the OTP manually or contact our support.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>